title: Watch Vulcan Centaur rocket launch 'neighborhood watch' satellites for the US military early on Feb. 12
description: A Vulcan Centaur rocket will launch a pair of space surveillance satellites for the U.S. Space Force early Thursday (Feb. 12), and you can watch the action live.
